Create any list of items that you want and make it as large as you need.
When it comes time to export the data, choose the format that works best for the data in your list.
Remember the details and use the Data Settings tab in this program to match the list you are importing.
Here are some examples from our ILS:
CALL #(ITEM)|TITLE|BARCODE
"CALL #(ITEM)"|"AUTHOR"|"TITLE"|"BARCODE"
"CALL #(ITEM)","BARCODE","245|a"
CALL #(ITEM)|BARCODE|AUTHOR|TITLE
